e":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2edd0f23fc56dcba9e245e9247a52764b778529e","tid":1252192,"uid":85629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b9abcf4e64b64b50696ff8aec9e1e48b59754cd4","tid":1252192,"uid":267640,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"要斷絕外國勢力介入，要斷絕外國武器/裝備供給，長遠黎睇D狗罩就會失效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"用強国貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過可能本身已經有毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"以後唔洗衝<br />\n未打都已經毒瓜晒班狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1014e222f437efd62ae4350079283d41baffaf","tid":1252192,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"制裁佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c328cd22ae3e5b1f0c10125a9fda024f0aa4ad","tid":1252192,"uid":12185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"寫信俾各大加拿大報紙叫佢地調查吓係咪真係呢間公司做？<br />\nTemplate:<br />\n<br />\nTitle: <strong>News Tips on Canadian Arms Transfer to Hong Kong</strong><br />\n<br />\nTo whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to ask if your company could investigate and report the following issue-<br />\n<br />\nIt has been found that in the recent government crackdown of the anti-extradition protests in Hong Kong, riot police are using gas masks that are possibly made by the Canadian defense company AirBoss of America. Attached are some pictures that show similarities between the Canada-made air mask and those used by Hong Kong police.<br />\n<br />\nIs it possible for your company to contact AirBoss to confirm whether it is exporting arms to Hong Kong?<br />\n<br />\nThis issue is important, as the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Canada has already issued a statement in solidarity with the Hong Kong people (<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/global-affairs/news/2019/06/statement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fglobal-affairs%2Fnews%2F2019%2F06%2Fstatement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0b78c56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/global-affairs/news/2019/06/statement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html</a>). There might be suspicions of hypocrisy if it is found that Canada is verbally supporting the movement but arming the government to suppress the people on the side.<br />\n<br />\nBest,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你個名</span><br />\n<br />\nAirBoss website on C4 CBRN gas masks: <a href=\"https://airbossofamerica.com/engineered-products/defense/products/cbrn/c4_cbrn_gas_mask.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fairbossofamerica.com%2Fengineered-products%2Fdefense%2Fproducts%2Fcbrn%2Fc4_cbrn_gas_mask.php&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=028b2ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://airbossofamerica.com/engineered-products/defense/products/cbrn/c4_cbrn_gas_mask.php</a><br />\n<br />\nPictures of Hong Kong crackdown:<br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">記得將樓主幾幅圖塞喺度做附件</span>）<br />\nSources: Mingpao (picture 1), HK01 (picture 2), Hong Kong Free Press (picture 3)."},{"pid":"ab61d8912fadcfd0e40bb5be823fb4ad57d4b847","tid":1252192,"uid":264926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d28b776e21883461ee3037f5898b05e9136b7183","tid":1252192,"uid":6799,"like":119,"dislike":2,"score":117,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:19:26.000Z","msg":"可唔可以要求加拿大禁止出口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"人地禁止出口，到時gas mask 得返個殼，無個芯，變曬halloween面品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a38f226b3b3a777ba904af273f36f1d900d6c70","tid":1252192,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci