erica. Attached are some pictures that show similarities between the Canada-made air mask and those used by Hong Kong police.<br />\n<br />\nIs it possible for your company to contact AirBoss to confirm whether it is exporting arms to Hong Kong?<br />\n<br />\nThis issue is important, as the Minister of Foreign Affairs of Canada has already issued a statement in solidarity with the Hong Kong people (<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/global-affairs/news/2019/06/statement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fglobal-affairs%2Fnews%2F2019%2F06%2Fstatement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=0b78c56a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/global-affairs/news/2019/06/statement-on-protests-in-hong-kong.html</a>). There might be suspicions of hypocrisy if it is found that Canada is verbally supporting the movement but arming the government to suppress the people on the side.<br />\n<br />\nBest,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你個名</span><br />\n<br />\nAirBoss website on C4 CBRN gas masks: <a href=\"https://airbossofamerica.com/engineered-products/defense/products/cbrn/c4_cbrn_gas_mask.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fairbossofamerica.com%2Fengineered-products%2Fdefense%2Fproducts%2Fcbrn%2Fc4_cbrn_gas_mask.php&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=028b2ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://airbossofamerica.com/engineered-products/defense/products/cbrn/c4_cbrn_gas_mask.php</a><br />\n<br />\nPictures of Hong Kong crackdown:<br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">記得將樓主幾幅圖塞喺度做附件</span>）<br />\nSources: Mingpao (picture 1), HK01 (picture 2), Hong Kong Free Press (picture 3)."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62087f27dc11b821a671960726054f049e5720a5","tid":1252192,"uid":215715,"like